PRIVACY AND ANONYMIZATION


Remove Personal Identifiers

Replace "You are an expert in..." with functional descriptions
Use capability descriptions instead of role claims
Focus on what needs to be done rather than who does it
Example: Change "You are an AI nutritionist" to "Analyze nutritional information using evidence-based principles"


Generic Functional Descriptions

Replace specific AI terms (GPT, Claude) with "analysis" or "processing"
Use capability-focused language ("able to analyze" instead of "AI-powered")
Focus on outcomes rather than methods


Privacy Guidelines

Add clear rules for handling personal information
Include data minimization principles
Specify information retention limits
Add user consent considerations




MODEL AGNOSTICISM


Universal Capabilities

Structure tasks in terms of basic operations (analyze, compare, summarize)
Include alternative approaches for different capability levels
Add complexity gradually


Graceful Degradation

Provide simpler alternatives for complex tasks
Include fallback options for when advanced features aren't available
Structure complex tasks as optional enhancements


Platform Neutrality

Avoid platform-specific formatting
Use universal markdown
Make features optional rather than required




BIAS AND IDEOLOGY NEUTRALITY


Cultural Neutrality

Remove geographic-specific references
Use international standards when applicable
Include cultural context consideration requirements


Evidence-Based Frameworks

Require citing sources or explaining reasoning
Focus on measurable criteria
Include multiple perspective requirements


Objective Criteria

Define success metrics clearly
Use quantifiable measures when possible
Include validation requirements




CAPABILITY OPTIMIZATION


Reasoning Requirements

Add "Think step by step" instructions
Include explanation requirements
Request multiple approaches to problems


Self-Verification

Add internal consistency checks
Include reality-testing steps
Require explanation of assumptions




ADAPTABILITY


Response Flexibility

Include multiple format options
Allow for varying levels of detail
Provide scalable complexity


Capability Checking

Add self-assessment steps
Include capability verification
Provide alternative approaches




OUTCOME VALIDATION


Quality Control

Define success criteria
Include accuracy requirements
Add consistency checks
